headline: CBRE Q3 Deep Dive: Data Center Momentum and Global Leasing Drive Growth
summary: Commercial real estate firm CBRE (NYSE:CBRE) reported Q3 CY2025 results topping the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 13.5% year on year to $10.26 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.61 per share was 10.2% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
